Let’s talk auto buy authors! I have dozens of authors I’ll purchase anything from. They could’ve written an instruction manual and I’d buy it. These authors may sometimes have stories that aren’t my favorite but I’ll forever buy any book with their name on it. 

Some auto buy authors are:
@marykubica 
@riley.sager 
@ruthwarewriter 
@lisajewelluk 
@tjenkinsreid 
@ashleywinsteadbooks 

I’m going to HAVE to do a part two here but I’d love to know who your auto buy authors are below!

This is quickly becoming a favorite theme of mine. No matter what these authors write and no matter how I have to get it, I will be reading it. Library, kindle, ARC, paying full price… nothing is too much for these authors and their art. Your comments in the first part helped inspire this second part!

I love all things by:
@alicewriterland 
@alex.michaelides 
@johnmarrs.author 
@launger 
@sharilapena 
@smariedowning 

Tell me your auto buy/auto read authors!!
